# Akan Name Finder
Project Description
The Akan Name Finder is a web application that calculates your Akan name based on your birthdate and gender. Akan names are derived from Ghanaian culture, where children are often named based on the day of the week they were born. This app provides users with a fun and interactive way to discover their unique Akan name.

## Features
Input your birthdate: year, month, and day.
Select your gender: male or female.
Display the corresponding Akan name based on the entered data.
Alerts users for invalid inputs (e.g., invalid dates or missing gender selection).
How It Works
Users enter their birthdate and gender.
The app calculates the day of the week using Zeller's Congruence.
The Akan name is determined based on the day of the week and the selected gender.
The Akan name is displayed dynamically on the screen.
### Technologies Used
HTML5: Structure and layout of the application.
CSS3: Styling for a visually appealing user interface.
JavaScript: Logic for calculations and dynamic interactions.

