https://github.com/ly441/akan-names.git




##### Business Development Document (BDD)
Behavior	Input Example	Expected Output
Input birthdate and gender	Year: 1995, Month: 8, Day: 15, Male	"Your Akan name is Kwabena"
Input invalid day	Year: 1995, Month: 8, Day: 35	Alert: "Invalid date. Please check your inputs."
No gender selected	Year: 1995, Month: 8, Day: 15	Alert: "Please fill out all fields correctly."

