Landing Page Description:
Discover Your Unique Akan Name
Welcome to the Akan Name Finder! In Ghanaian culture, a child’s name often reflects the day of the week they were born. This app allows you to uncover your Akan name by simply entering your birthdate and gender. It’s a fun and cultural way to learn something new about yourself!

How It Works:

Enter your birth year, month, and day in the form.
Select your gender (Male or Female).
Hit the Submit button to find out your Akan name and its significance.
Explore your roots and connect with a piece of Ghanaian tradition. Try it now and share your Akan name with friends and family!







